  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948490/extras/8e03004cf1f4d251cf308d457abe82b7.poster.avif?t=1758206929\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948490/extras/8e03004cf1f4d251cf308d457abe82b7.webm?t=1758206929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948490/extras/8e03004cf1f4d251cf308d457abe82b7.mp4?t=1758206929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Concept</h2>Xion Leak is a fast and frantic <strong>two-player co-op game</strong>!<br>Speed up your times to earn <strong>gold and silver trophies!</strong><br><br>Run fast, sync up, and avoid the countless dangers that the mysterious Foreman has placed in your path.<br><br>In some levels, the stopwatch is replaced by dangerous <strong>XION gas that destroys everything in its path.</strong><br>Put the pedal to the metal and stay ahead of the XION gas before it fries your precious circuits!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948490/extras/b2a1a0083fa688d0b09337b8d671f0cb.poster.avif?t=1758206929\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948490/extras/b2a1a0083fa688d0b09337b8d671f0cb.webm?t=1758206929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948490/extras/b2a1a0083fa688d0b09337b8d671f0cb.mp4?t=1758206929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Timed levels to <strong>earn trophies</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Puzzle</strong> levels to <strong>solve together</strong><br></li><li> Pick up the pace to stay ahead of the gas in deadly <strong>XION levels</strong><br></li><li> Over <strong>60 levels</strong> spread across <strong>3 biomes</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Customize your robots</strong> with wacky hats<br></li><li> Pixel art graphics and a fun, full-throttled feel <br></li><li> A piston-pumping soundtrack with drum & bass, electro...</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948490/extras/22ff9fd619f4ea8689dbbcc2ed97ec73.poster.avif?t=1758206929\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948490/extras/22ff9fd619f4ea8689dbbcc2ed97ec73.webm?t=1758206929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948490/extras/22ff9fd619f4ea8689dbbcc2ed97ec73.mp4?t=1758206929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
